Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.15,B2,FEMALE SPIRIT,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.91,B2,REAPER,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.98,B2,SOUL REAPER,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.47,B2,SOUL REAPER,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.27,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,With all these missing\NSoul Reaper incidents going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.60,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want\Nto do this, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:14.08,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Going out without a gigai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.82,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to you,\Ndon't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't make me transport\Nyour merchandise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:25.04,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you've been such\Na huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.93,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to these recent incidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.95,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my usual\Nroute anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.17,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That put me in a real bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why there's\Nso much here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.84,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm willing to give\Nyou some good deals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:39.55,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.47,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:47.09,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We're all ready to go, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.26,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm done here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.26,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.03,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to leave on our
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.53,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara's Shop employee vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.65,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.56,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,we had nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.72,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,because we were sold\Nout of merchandise,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.49,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,so I planned a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.68,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,But now that we have\Nall this merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:12.86,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,We should get right to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.88,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll go on that\Nvacation, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.05,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.07,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll excuse us,\Nwe'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.14,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.74,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I went around to several of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.02,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,places where the incidents occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.32,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,There was evidence that the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.74,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers were attacked\Nand probably eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:39.99,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Then they were attacked\Nby Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.80,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,No, they weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.90,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,At the sites,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.79,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,there was absolutely no residual\NSpiritual Pressure from Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.17,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.91,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough, Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.59,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.30,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel like eating\Na Soul Reaper like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.26,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Dance Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.28,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.30,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So it was targeting Soul Reapers,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.73,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.16,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.24,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,You remember me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.55,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.52,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one, the only,\NSoul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.45,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,in charge of Karakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.42,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Zennosuke Kurumadani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:22.71,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the guy who\Ntook over for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.27,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,This...has no effect on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.15,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this Spiritual Pressure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.31,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just as Urahara said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.36,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different in some way\Nfrom that of a Hollow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:44.99,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.66,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.26,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,That technique... I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.41,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I knew if I went on a rampage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.25,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,in this town, you'd appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.83,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,And I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You know me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.64,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.15,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.41,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.38,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.71,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Shrieker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.55,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be! That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,you fell into the depths of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.86,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Zanpakuto can only\Nwash away sins{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}committed after one's death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.18,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for Hollows who\Ncommitted major sins{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.37,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when they were still humans,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hell will open its gates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:37.18,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You! How did you get out of Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:42.23,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,How? I'm not going\Nto tell you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.55,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.31,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall for the\Nsame trick twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.50,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.41,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Nice moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.17,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't recall\Nyou being that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.10,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.30,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I had simply lost my\Npowers back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.72,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,I will assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.47,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.47,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.06,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.44,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.42,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.92,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.09,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make\Nit a painful death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.76,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:03.37,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His power and speed are at\Nan entirely different level!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.92,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.04,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.20,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A chain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.95,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,This chain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.05,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,can't be cut by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.35,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.56,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.63,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai Tsukishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.51,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That takes care of his clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.12,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.02,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is that possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.59,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't sense the presence\Nof any of his clones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.06,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did those bombs\Ncome from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.04,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.44,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.91,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tsuchinamazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.09,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.43,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.14,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was an escape technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:07.56,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumadani!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.41,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has leech bombs\Nin his body, as well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.45,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,My entire body is like a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.96,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.99,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... Get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:33.70,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:43.80,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different from the\Nway I was back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.39,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What...are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:53.48,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what\Nthis chain is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.93,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,This chain is from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.95,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,And I am a Sinner of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,"Sinner"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.93,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a Sinner\Ncould escape from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.52,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,But I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.07,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,To get my revenge on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.05,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.16,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.11,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.19,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.56,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.90,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We got a report from the Department\Nof Research and Development
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:44.37,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,about some weird Spiritual Pressure\Nbeing detected in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.55,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.37,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Sinner of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.73,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,A Sinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.08,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.75,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.42,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere when things\Nwere just getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.15,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.61,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,One Soul Reaper down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:35.78,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai! Hihio Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.71,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hikotsu Taiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.69,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be enough to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:14.16,B2,SHRIEKER,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep returning from\Nthe depths of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.14,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:27.93,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:40.65,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the emergency\NCaptains' Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:45.53,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Captains Zaraki and Kurotsuchi\Ndon't seem to be here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.98,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.03,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I summoned you all here\Non short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:54.57,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Fill in the absent captains\Nwith the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.54,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we received\Nword a short while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:02.92,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,that a Sinner of Hell appeared\Nin the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.58,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sinner of Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:14.26,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,"Sinner"? That's a reference\Nto a resident of Hell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.92,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of people who die
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:21.20,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,are sent to the Soul Society,\Nthe home of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:26.69,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,However, souls of people who\Ncommitted heinous acts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.29,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,during their lifetimes\Nare unable to enter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.15,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Society and are\Ninstead plunged into Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.49,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.46,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,As Sinners, they are\Ntied in chains
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.50,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,and condemned for all\Neternity for their sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.03,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time in the history
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.78,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,of the Soul Society that a Sinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.53,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,a resident of Hell,\Nhas found his way back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.28,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,into the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.77,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean something\Nis amiss in Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.60,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.26,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,There's the gatekeeper in\NHell called Kushanaada,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.48,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,whose control is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.85,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.77,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,However, I've heard that there\Nare powerful beings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.01,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,with mysterious powers\Nwho make their home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.70,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,deep in the bowels of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.80,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,If they are able to freely find
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.51,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,their way into the\NWorld of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.96,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,we've got a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.36,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.87,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We will start by dispatching
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.47,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai and Rukia Kuchiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:38.26,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,who first encountered the Sinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.09,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,as advance troops to the\NWorld of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.89,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,In the event the need arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.89,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I will provide them\Nwith procedures to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.48,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,infiltrate Hell and to make\Nan emergency return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.97,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we request\Nthe assistance of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.99,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper\NIchigo Kurosaki, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.62,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,No, we mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:04.04,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Give strict orders to both\NAbarai and Kuchiki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:09.29,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,that they are not to involve\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.36,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,under any circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:35.36,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,Szayelaporro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.03,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Aaroniero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:46.04,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed there was another person\Nfalling along side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.77,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,But it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.90,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that's\None tough cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.41,B2,AAERONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hoping it would break?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.38,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.78,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that if it had cracked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:06.39,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I could open it up and investigate\Nthe liquid inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.30,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.02,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what this place is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.86,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,but it's convenient that\NLord Aizen isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:19.82,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,You can live on inside me after\Nmy Glotoneria eats you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:20.74,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.45,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,You just said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.02,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't know what this place is."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:31.10,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, shouldn't we investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:35.25,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,where we are, rather\Nthan kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.46,B2,AARONIERO B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:43.22,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,I can investigate that\Nafter I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.80,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to comprehend\Nthe difference in our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.71,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I am Espada Number 8,\Nand you are 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.69,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.15,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.86,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,You two are funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.40,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.93,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.91,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.92,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.38,B2,AARONIERO B,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come\Ndown and talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.90,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.30,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. This is Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.39,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.97,B2,AARONIERO A,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of nonsense is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.28,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.82,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for jogging\Nmy memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.23,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,It appears I did die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:38.65,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that damned\Ndespicable Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.33,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.61,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to get\Nout of this place
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.62,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,you call Hell and return\Nto Hueco Mundo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.79,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.14,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.50,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a way, it's better\Nif you didn't keep it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.66,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shuren.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.68,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:11.18,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to survive here\Nin Hell is to do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.89,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:14.35,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Taikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:15.81,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Gunjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.27,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Garogai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.14,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Our guests appear dissatisfied\Nwith Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.49,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach them\Nto appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.37,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Aaroniero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.68,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,A Gran Rey Cero, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.95,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of\Nan Espada's Cero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.39,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.69,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:03.69,B2,SZAYELAPORRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so cocky, Sinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:14.88,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Their level of power was nowhere\Nnear enough to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.02,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Gunjo, what about the man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.45,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,we sent to the World\Nof the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.62,B2,GUNJO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! He returned safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.85,B2,GUNJO,0000,0000,0000,,He was no longer of use,\Nso I silenced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.92,B2,GUNJO,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.18,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:36.66,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,Our dark days are about\Nto come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:41.61,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected,\Nit looks like it has to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:46.78,B2,SHUREN,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring you down,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.00,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.97,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Now let us return to\Nthe Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.31,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm glad no one else\Ngot hurt besides us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:32.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Let's just hope nothing\Nelse happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:34.00,B2,KURUMADANI,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumadani Ze-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:42.03,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun in Hawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:45.85,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a blast using the money\Nwe put away and saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:48.78,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We'll enjoy the beach\Nand shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:50.55,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,This is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:52.82,B2,STAFF,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:56.49,B2,STAFF,0000,0000,0000,,What is this cat?\NWhere'd it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:00.79,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kisuke! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:04.54,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought we could\Nsave on Yoruichi's airfare.